---
import Container from "./Container.astro"
---

<div id="features">
  <Container>
    <div class="md:w-2/3 lg:w-1/2">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary">
        <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M9 4.5a.75.75 0 01.721.544l.813 2.846a3.75 3.75 0 002.576 2.576l2.846.813a.75.75 0 010 1.442l-2.846.813a3.75 3.75 0 00-2.576 2.576l-.813 2.846a.75.75 0 01-1.442 0l-.813-2.846a3.75 3.75 0 00-2.576-2.576l-2.846-.813a.75.75 0 010-1.442l2.846-.813A3.75 3.75 0 007.466 7.89l.813-2.846A.75.75 0 019 4.5zM18 1.5a.75.75 0 01.728.568l.258 1.036c.236.94.97 1.674 1.91 1.91l1.036.258a.75.75 0 010 1.456l-1.036.258c-.94.236-1.674.97-1.91 1.91l-.258 1.036a.75.75 0 01-1.456 0l-.258-1.036c-.236-.94-.97-1.674-1.91-1.91l-1.036-.258a.75.75 0 010-1.456l1.036-.258c.94-.236 1.674-.97 1.91-1.91l.258-1.036A.75.75 0 0118 1.5zM16.5 15a.75.75 0 01.712.513l.394 1.183c.15.447.5.799.948.948l1.183.394a.75.75 0 010 1.424l-1.183.394a1.875 1.875 0 00-.948.948l-.394 1.183a.75.75 0 01-1.424 0l-.394-1.183a1.875 1.875 0 00-.948-.948l-1.183-.394a.75.75 0 010-1.424l1.183-.394a1.875 1.875 0 00.948-.948l.394-1.183A.75.75 0 0116.5 15z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
      </svg>
      
      <h2 class="my-8 text-2xl font-bold text-gray-700 dark:text-white md:text-4xl">
        Tecnologia da Studio, <br/> concepita per il Live.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg">Platinum non è un semplice player, è un ecosistema mossa dall'Intelligenza Artificiale per risolvere i problemi reali di ogni serata.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-16 grid divide-x divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-700 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 text-gray-600 dark:border-gray-700 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 lg:divide-y-0 xl:grid-cols-4">
      
      <!-- Feature 1: IA Separation -->
      <div class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
        <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
          <div class="text-cyan-500 text-4xl">🧠</div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary">AI Stem Separation</h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">Estrai voce e base da qualsiasi video in meno di 60 secondi. Sfrutta la potenza della tua GPU NVIDIA per una qualità audio da studio di registrazione.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 2: Radar RMS -->
      <div class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
        <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
          <div class="text-purple-500 text-4xl">📡</div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary">Radar RMS Anti-Garbage</h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">Il primo sistema che "ascolta" il video e taglia automaticamente pubblicità e silenzi finali tipici dei video scaricati da YouTube.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 3: Smart Booking -->
      <div class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
        <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
          <div class="text-green-500 text-4xl">📲</div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary">Smart Booking QR</h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">Addio foglietti di carta. I tuoi clienti scansionano il QR Code, sfogliano il tuo catalogo e si prenotano direttamente dal loro smartphone.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Feature 4: Audio Rack -->
      <div class="group relative bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
        <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
          <div class="text-orange-500 text-4xl">🎛️</div>
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary">Rack Audio DSP</h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm">Compressore dinamico e Turbo Boost +6dB. Mantieni un volume di uscita costante e cristallino per tutta la durata dell'evento.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</div>
